Mode.description:
Summary:
     Run Tesseract only - fastest
TesseractOnly = 0,

 Summary:
     Run just the LSTM line recognizer.
LstmOnly = 1,

 Summary:
     Run the LSTM recognizer, but allow fallback to Tesseract when things get difficult.
TesseractLstmCombined = 2,

 Summary:
     Specify this mode when calling init_*(), to indicate that any of the above modes
     should be automatically inferred from the variables in the language-specific
     config, command-line configs, or if not specified in any of the above should
     be set to the default OEM_TESSERACT_ONLY.
 Default = 3
